    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite all 13 credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels and 6 factors not assessed, the submission is accepted at this stage pending remediation plan. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on hemolysis power-law coefficients provides partial coverage of model input uncertainty. The assessment team notes that the ContextOfUse prose adequately describes operating conditions (5 flow-speed combinations, Class III VAD envelope) and that no structured applicability constraints or operating envelope links are required under the current review protocol. Remediation of the six not-assessed factors is required prior to regulatory submission.",
